Quickstrike:




Quickstrike turned his head to the explosion. He jolted. He was glad 
he wasn't near it. The Maximals had ran off, but he still wanted a 
fight. 

It was too late for that now. His chance was over. It was now time to 
get back to base...without the others. He looked up at the leaving 
ship. He frowned. He was fine without them anyhow.
